Amy Kwolek https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amy_Kwolek 0 Amy Kwolek (born Amy Kwoleková, 7 May 1986) is an English actress, who is best known for her role as Nadine in Girls in Love (2003–05) which has been an incredible success. Kwolek has also starred in Doctors (soap opera) (2005) and Casualty (TV series) (2008). Amy studied drama theatre arts at the University of Birmingham. She can currently be seen in cult sitcom Becoming Batman. Amy appears in Anonymous as Young Anne de Vere released in October 2011.
